To build the guides:

* Install source-highlighter (http://www.gnu.org/software/src-highlite/source-highlight.html)
* Install the mizuho gem (http://github.com/FooBarWidget/mizuho/tree/master)
* Run `rake guides` from the railties directory

Gem list installed:


actionmailer (2.2.2)
actionpack (2.2.2)
activerecord (2.2.2)
activeresource (2.2.2)
activesupport (2.2.2)
faker (0.3.1)
json (1.1.3)
populator (0.2.5)
rails (2.2.2)
rake (0.8.3)
rspec (1.1.11)
shooting_star (3.2.7)
simple-rss (1.1)